If you have spiritual gifts please do not let people make you feel like you are crazy. For a very long time before I really found myself and stepped into my power people around me would make it seem like the things I sensed wrong because of how I use to react to the energy. I’m a Cancer and would go emotionally off the deep end because I knew something but just couldn’t prove it or say how I knew it . I still battle with this at times but instead I transmute the anger into magic to manifest . If something felt off with a person, place, or thing I knew it . To this day people try to insult my intelligence knowing I read for people that I’ve never met a day in my life,  seen their faces, or seen them in person. Many of my clients live in different states, continents, and countries. If you are like me , you are not crazy beloved . Practice  solitude until your soul tribe finds you . The ones that won’t judge you and the ones you can relate to. They don’t have to be spiritual either a lot of my good friends accept me and love me . Isolate for a bit and tap into your gifts . I promise you will see the world and people very differently .  Blessed be 🖤🌙
